metadata.name: stuffy
metadata.description:
After a hot and humid day, "she" can relax in an empty classroom.
She sweats more than most people, so she makes sure no one is around to wipe away the sweat.
I made sure no one was there and was relaxing when I ran into a classmate.
What will happen to her after this, when she is left in a daze due to a combination of heat and surprise?

I hope you will support me so I can paint the rest of these girls!
